<template>
  <v-container class="pl-16 pr-16">
    <v-toolbar color="deep-purple lighten-2" dark class="mt-10">
      <v-toolbar-title>测试信息</v-toolbar-title>
    </v-toolbar>
    <form class="pa-12 grey lighten-5 mt-8">

      <v-select
          :items="courseList"
          v-model="testInfo.courseName"
          label="课程名称"
      ></v-select>
      <v-text-field
          v-model="testInfo.name"
          label="测试名称"
      ></v-text-field>
      <v-text-field
          v-model="testInfo.startTime"
          label="起始时间"
      ></v-text-field>
      <v-text-field
          v-model="testInfo.endTime"
          label="结束时间"
      ></v-text-field>
      <v-select
          :items="formatLengthList"
          v-model="testInfo.length"
          label="题目数量"
      ></v-select>
      <v-text-field
          disabled label="题目列表"
          :value="questionIdList"
      ></v-text-field>

      <v-btn class="ml-0 mt-8 "  color="indigo" dark disabled>
        确认
      </v-btn>
    </form>
    <v-toolbar color="deep-purple lighten-2" dark class="mt-10 mb-10">
      <v-toolbar-title>题目</v-toolbar-title>
    </v-toolbar>
    <v-row v-for="ques in questionList" :key="ques.id">
      <question-item
          :key="ques.id"
          :teacher-id="ques.teacherId"
          :course-id="ques.courseId"
          :content="ques.content"
          :analysis="ques.analysis"
          :answer="ques.answer"
          :ques-id="ques.id"
          :type="ques.type"
          :show-analysis="showAnalysis"
      ></question-item>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script lang="ts">
import Vue from "vue";
import QuestionItem from "../../components/QuestionItem.vue";
export default Vue.extend( {
  name: "TestEdit",
  components:{
    QuestionItem
  },
  data(){
    return{
      testInfo:{},
      courseList:[],
      questionList:[{id:1,courseId:1,teacherId:1,content:"DO?#~#A.yes#~#B.yes",
        analysis:"None",answer:"A",type:"单选"},
        {id:2,courseId: 2,teacherId: 1,
          content: "新世纪福音战士中，谁被称为国民homo？#~#A.碇真嗣 #~#B.碇源堂#~#C.渚薰#~#D.加持良治",
          analysis:"None",answer: "C",type:"单选"},
        {id:3,courseId: 2,teacherId: 1,
          content: "新世纪福音战士中，谁是女主？#~#A.明日香 #~#B.绫波丽#~#C.葛城美里#~#D.赤木律子#~#E.真希波",
          analysis:"None",answer: "ABCDE",type:"多选"},
        {id:4,courseId: 2,teacherId: 1,
          content: "新世纪福音战士中，____被量产机分尸，虽败犹荣",
          analysis:"None",answer: "二号机",type:"填空"},
        {id:5,courseId: 2,teacherId: 1,
          content: "以下哪一个选项是新世纪福音战士的经典op曲目？#~#A.残酷天使的行动纲领#~#B.使徒的行动纲领#~#C.福音战士的行动纲领",
          analysis:"None",answer: "A",type:"单选"},
      ],
      showAnalysis: true,
      questionIdList:[],
      formatLengthList:[5,10,20,25]
    }

  },
  mounted() {
    this.testInfo={id:1,name:"第一章测试",courseId:1,teacherId:1,courseName:"软件工程与计算",
      startTime:"2020-06-18 20：00：00",endTime:"2020-06-19 20：00：00",
      length:5,state:true
    };
    for(let i=0;i<this.questionList.length;i++){
      this.questionIdList.push(this.questionList[i].id)
    }
  },
  methods:{

  }
})
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
